♪ I'm just gonna walk home ♪

57
00:02:56,594 --> 00:02:59,513
♪ Kicking stones
at parked cars ♪

58
00:03:00,598 --> 00:03:02,808
♪ But I had a great night ♪

59
00:03:02,892 --> 00:03:05,019
