my home, this town.

96
00:05:22,906 --> 00:05:25,284
You think that some candy and
a keychain makes up for that?

97
00:05:26,493 --> 00:05:27,494
I was sad.

98
00:05:29,913 --> 00:05:31,790
People do crazy things
when they're sad.

99
00:05:34,585 --> 00:05:36,795
[ Water running ]

100
