is debts that you don't pay ♪

155
00:08:30,344 --> 00:08:31,637
♪ Pay, pay ♪

156
00:08:32,804 --> 00:08:35,015
♪ Well, you need
to make a quick call ♪

157
00:08:35,098 --> 00:08:37,726
♪ Just call it a loss,
but you can't just... ♪

158
